", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031634_644418450368664_1371992380768044124_n.png?_nc_cat=105&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=3R8uQzzhnywQ7kNvgEa_AhS&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCZi_KpNrLJEXcE1uK478Z9C_Lfok7Y5i6_fm7WlF_8Ww&oe=673349DD"}, {"file_name": "Transparent Logo.png", "id": "506259461036237", "image_type": "APP_IMG_LOGO_TRANSPARENT", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031410_506259464369570_1935699239410139863_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=DP6Ac7TCHnoQ7kNvgEmkS17&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYD_ahW9CvEYmp1XrBJjQ-KwfYzY0ZA6nbMyJ8UQ_WTFjQ&oe=67333DF0"}]}, "id": "491331773052388", "locale": "en_US", "screenshots": [{"file_name": "WTB_Oculus_Screenshot_01.png", "id": "1863703943980286", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982559_1863703953980285_5150022613821930785_n.png?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=i3q06VyrShQQ7kNvgFUkpVg&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCyVf8xIok1IcuePKY79oxW5aUBCLrxneibyh-HzvBFMA&oe=67332B34"}, {"file_name": "WTB_Oculus_Screenshot_02.png", "id": "810378986845344", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39035406_810378990178677_8434640169366727822_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NL4oOcjHfUwQ7kNvgFDzc3C&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAc62jt7N1x56EYE0Ze2eKiocQs2VHNxBy9zpdWs31nkQ&oe=67334506"}, {"file_name": "WTB_Oculus_Screenshot_03.png", "id": "652554983249060", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982540_652554993249059_6795154914079195543_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=WwSzawa3wzUQ7kNvgGLf4_S&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBP76npE03lSqTzdUWHlNvrRwRWDB1v5CWdy6rS4KvXcw&oe=673343EA"}, {"file_name": "WTB_Oculus_Screenshot_04.png", "id": "1271702740055339", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38974706_1271702750055338_8269122948003790085_n.png?_nc_cat=108&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=NxKtM8Af8pcQ7kNvgHcBA0e&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYC5zSf-qKpFBfLAmKtJPozS5OGbc7mO2NuPkW1hkXQxLw&oe=67333360"}, {"file_name": "WTB_Oculus_Screenshot_05.png", "id": "828696395103254", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031359_828696401769920_57076814273176680_n.png?_nc_cat=103&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=FS0PdZx__GcQ7kNvgG6BURd&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCiPKtqtiEhux7T1_YGxpJhG4f-hoYPbJlS6KPYqQbm5g&oe=67332B17"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "WTB Trailer Thumbnail.png", "id": "440671491299687", "uri": "https://scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982541_440671494633020_8514066159405942550_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=5fkVw6pxjhQQ7kNvgE0jzdu&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAbzBEdv_iXfCIIT_a2PBNjkfVc5VY1S4fQfH5am4RkKQ&oe=67333E61"}, "display_name": "WHAT THE BAT?", "keywords": ["funny", "parody", "casual", "physics", "sports"], "long_description": "A wise man once said: If all you have are bats for hands, everything feels like a baseball.\n\nFrom the creators of WHAT THE GOLF? comes a silly VR game about navigating life with baseball bats for hands. Swing your way through over 100 levels of batting, cooking, shooting, smashing, parking, painting, pickling, petting, and WHATnot. \n\nExperience fully immersive silliness in a first-person experience like no other!\n\nFeatures:\n- 100+ unique levels of physical comedy and craziness!\n- Wholesome original soundtrack!\n- Pet a dog, pickle a tractor, and take selfies with The Selfie Bat!\n- The expected playtime is 4 hours, but remember to take breaks (too much VR can drive you batty)\n", "short_description": "You have bats for hands - now GO! Swing through a series of increasingly silly minigames in a slapstick VR comedy that\u2019s about so much more than baseball. \n"}, {"images": {"nodes": []}, "id": "467270088759588", "locale": "it_IT", "screenshots": [], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "WHAT THE BAT?", "keywords": ["divertente", "parodia", "semplice", "fisica", "sport"], "long_description": "\"Una volta, un uomo saggio disse: se tutto ci\u00f2 che hai sono delle mazze al posto delle mani, tutto sembra una palla da baseball.\n \nDai creatori di WHAT THE GOLF?, ecco un simpatico gioco in realt\u00e0 virtuale in cui affronterai la vita con delle mazze al posto delle mani. Fatti strada agitando le tue mazze attraverso oltre 100 livelli in cui dovrai prendere a mazzate, cucinare, distruggere, parcheggiare, dipingere, mettere sottaceto, accarezzare e molto altro ancora. \n \nVivi una simpatica esperienza in prima persona completamente immersiva unica nel suo genere!\n \nCaratteristiche:\n- Pi\u00f9 di 100 livelli unici di commedia fisica e follie!\n- Piacevolissima colonna sonora originale!\n- Accarezza un cane, metti un trattore sottaceto e fatti un selfie con la mazza per selfie!\n- Il tempo di gioco stimato \u00e8 di 4 ore, ma ricorda di fare delle pause (troppa realt\u00e0 virtuale pu\u00f2 ammazzarti il cervello)\"", "short_description": "Hai delle mazze al posto delle mani: adesso VAI! Prendi a mazzate gli obiettivi attraverso una serie di minigiochi sempre pi\u00f9 sciocchi in una commedia grossolana in realt\u00e0 virtuale dove potrai fare molto di pi\u00f9 che giocare a baseball. "}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.whatthegames.com/what-the-bat-privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Triband", "support_website_url": "https://what-the-bat-faq.groovehq.com/help", "website_url": "https://www.whatthebat.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "2776542286000603"}], "external_subscription_t